[Act 30 of 2023 wef 30/10/2023]
(2)Despite any other provision in this Part, the following expenditure incurred by a TenthSchedule entity during the period between 1 January 2020 and 31 December 2020 (both dates inclusive) is allowed as a deduction for the relevant year of assessment:
