(4)Despite anything in this Act but subject to subsections (4A) and (5) and sections13(1)(r), (ra) and (rb) and 40A, tax at the rate of 15% is to be levied and paid on the gross amount of any income accruing in or derived from Singapore on or after 3 May 2002 from any profession or vocation carried on by—
